com.paypal.selion.platform.html

Interface ParentTraits

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractContainer, BasicPageImpl, Container

    public interface ParentTraits
    A generic interface for outlining the Parent traits of an HTML entity in SeLion.
    By Default, A Page BasicPageImpl is the parent to AbstractElement when loaded via SeLion. A parent can also be a AbstractContainer
